  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The HEMO-TIN trial is designed to look at both the safety (bleeding risk) and effectiveness
      (clotting risk) of tinzaparin compared with unfractionated heparin for anticoagulation in
      hemodialysis patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
